    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You are a Gemwielder, capable of controlling ancient artifacts called Gembearers. Powerful by themselves, only by socketing them with magical gems will you acquire powerful abilities that allow you to prevail in a duel with another Gemwielder.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Replayability</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game you adapt to the cards that appear and craft a new deck with a unique color combination. <strong>No two games are the same</strong> and whoever seizes the opportunities presented to them best, will be rewarded.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interaction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gemwielders is <strong>designed around interaction</strong> from the ground up. The innovative combat system allows the attack and defense cards to clash each turn and interact meaningfully.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Deckbuilder</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gemwielders will offer <strong>intense card battling duels</strong> against your friends and players around the world. The demo features local multiplayer and a single player practice mode to learn the game and experiment.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Release</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full game release is scheduled for 2025, introducing <strong>online multiplayer</strong>, more playable characters and new gem types. After release, new content will be added regularily.</p>",
